title: 이달의소녀탐구 #527 (LOONA TV #527)
members: Kim Lip, JinSoul, Go Won, Chuu
summary:
0:01 -- Kim Lip does an Aegyo face. She says they are headed to KCON LA.
0:15 -- Kim Lip: "We OEC have been to LA before but we were bummed we couldn't meet any of our fans". She confirms this with JinSoul who says that they did.
0:27 -- She turns the camera towards Go Won who is also sitting in the car with them. "Right Go Won?" Chuu and Go Won then recount their experience in LA. They talk until the end of the episode.
